curves.name: sect163r1
curves.desc: A randomly generated curve, using the SECG/X9.62 method. 'However for historical reasons the method used to generate E from S differs slightly from the method described in ANSI X9.62 [X9.62]. Specifically the coefficient b produced from S is the reverse of the coefficient that would have been produced by the method described in ANSI X9.62.'
